messages.content: What is the purpose of ComfyUI_toyxyz_test_nodes?
ComfyUI_toyxyz_test_nodes is a custom node that enables sending a webcam/screen to ComfyUI in real-time.
What is the recommended use case for ComfyUI_toyxyz_test_nodes?
This node is recommended for use with LCM/SDXL turbo.
What updates were made to ComfyUI_toyxyz_test_nodes on 2024/08/11?
The Direct_screenCap node was added to ComfyUI_toyxyz_test_nodes on 2024/08/11.
What features were added to ComfyUI_toyxyz_test_nodes on 2023/11/24?
On 2023/11/24, the following features were added to ComfyUI_toyxyz_test_nodes: Save image to path node, Render preview, Export video, and Face detection.
What changes were made to ComfyUI_toyxyz_test_nodes on 2023/11/29?
On 2023/11/29, Region Capture was added and the Webcam app UI was made smaller in ComfyUI_toyxyz_test_nodes.
What was added to ComfyUI_toyxyz_test_nodes on 2023/12/1?
Ai render overlay was added to ComfyUI_toyxyz_test_nodes on 2023/12/1.
To install ComfyUI_toyxyz_test_nodes, you need to git clone the repo to the ComfyUI/custom_nodes path and run setup.bat in 'ComfyUI/custom_nodes/ComfyUI_toyxyz_test_nodes/CaptureCam'.
